# Building

In order to build the `local-daemon` component, you must have the [go-zeromq/zmq4](https://github.com/go-zeromq/zmq4) repository cloned in your `$GOPATH`. 
``` sh
go get github.com/go-zeromq/zmq4
```

You also must intsall the `pkg-config` utility:
``` sh
apt-get install pkg-config
```

You may also require the following go modules to be installed:
``` sh
go get github.com/grpc-ecosystem/grpc-opentracing/go/otgrpc@v0.0.0-20180507213350-8e809c8a8645
go get google.golang.org/grpc@v1.50.1
go get google.golang.org/grpc/internal/channelz@v1.50.1
go get google.golang.org/grpc/internal/transport@v1.50.1
```